      "content": "hope? how can there be hope when the thing that defined me is gone? i was a scientist. i was a truth seeker. now i'm just a fraud who wasted two decades on a delusion. there's no \"resilience\" in being a failure. everyone I worked with knows. the whole field knows. i just want the feeling of being a lie to stop.",
