    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a mistake though. it's deeper than that. when your entire sense of reality is built on a fallacy, you realize you don't actually know how to exist. i've spent my whole life pursuing something that wasn't there. i'm just tired of the noise of pretending everything is okay when i know it's all just... empty. there's no version of the future where this doesn't feel like a total hollow joke.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
